</td>
<td style="vertical-align:middle; border:none; padding:0.08em;" class="nowrap"><p style="margin:0pt;"><b>(<span id="math_Eq.2" class="reference nourlexpansion" style="font-weight:bold;">Eq.2</span>)</b></p>
