<p>From here, due to the <a href="/wiki/Convolution_theorem" title="Convolution theorem">convolution theorem</a>, we can also view <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle |{\hat {x}}_{T}(f)|^{2}}">
